data.description: Looking for a classic beauty at the shore with all the amenities of modern living' You found it. This excellent opportunity offers 5 bedrooms with 3 ? and 1 2  bathrooms. This well-maintained home is generously proportioned with a flexible layout. 1st. floor offers an open floor plan to the bright dining living room area with a contemporary gas fireplace, oversized windows to let the natural light in, Laminate flooring throughout the house, modern style kitchen with granite counter tops and stainless-steel appliances, ceramic flooring, the doorway at the end of the kitchen leads to 2 nicely sized bedrooms and 1 full bath and a kitchenette area to create a mother-in-law suite if desired. In the rear of the house off the kitchen leads to a generously sized laundry room with storage area and a half bath. 2 ND floor is the enormous Primary bedroom with a desirable master bath, a walk-in closet, patio sliding doors to capture the summer breeze. Across the hall are 2 more large bedrooms and a room that could be used as office space or storage area. The fenced in yard is big enough for all your outdoor entertaining, room to add a pool for those hot summer days. Located within a short distance are the stores and shopping centers, restaurants, eateries for all your needs. The beach ramp and boardwalk are within minutes away. Property is being sold in AS-IS condition. Seller to provide a passing North Wildwood Zoning and Fire Permit.
